channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: Oscar Mayer Wienermobile Crashes Along Chicago Area Highway
item.description: The hot dog-shaped vehicle hit a car Monday morning and its driver lost control and overcorrected, causing it to roll onto its side on I-294.

item.title: What is the UK's two-child benefit cap and what is Labour's position on it
item.description: Keir Starmer suspended seven Labour MPs after they backed an SNP amendment calling for the two-child benefit limit to be scrapped - here we look at what the 'cruel' policy is

item.title: Sharks ‘high on cocaine’ after drugs are being flushed down the loo
item.description: It could be affecting their behaviour making them more aggressive.

item.title: Thousands of people could be entitled to discounted or free TV Licence
item.description: The regular expense has always been controversial - but some households could be missing out on savings

item.title: Psychic who envisioned Trump assassination attempt gives his US election prediction
item.description: 'I wasn't expecting this to happen until at least August this year.'

item.title: Liz Truss goes on Fox News to dish out advice on winning elections
item.description: The ex-PM who was dumped by voters at the General Election went on Fox News where she slated Kamala Harris and warned that she'll be trounced by Donald Trump in November

item.title: 14 children end up in hospital after trying ‘adult only’ crisps
item.description: The 'R18' crisps are made using an extract from the ultra-spicy ghost pepper.

item.title: Three-bedroom home goes on sale for just £57k – but then people see the toilet
item.description: The house is described as an "investment" and is in need of a bit of modernisation - but it could be a great opportunity for someone wanting to get on the property ladder

item.title: Woman describes out of body aura she felt in near-death experience after crash
item.description: 'The experience has allowed me to see the beauty of life.'

item.title: Moon exploration makes stunning discovery, Chinese scientists reveal
item.description: Chinese scientists have made a stunning discovery during tests of samples taken from the Moon's surface as China look to bridge the gap in the space race with the US and Russia
